        {
            "title": "中國出口商轉嫁伊朗戰爭成本壓力 全球消費品通膨或將升溫",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"China's General Administration of Customs\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"632\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/E2CMAgsEW4qbF.BQ54cV8A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/b7b1162d6ab53e20bb8db0e467d3898e\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">China's General Administration of Customs</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 伊朗戰爭推高了與石油相關的投入成本，中國出口商開始上調從泳裝到空調等各類商品的價格，表明全球消費品通膨可能升溫。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博對Trade Data Monitor匯編的海關數據分析發現，3月份十幾個類別的消費品價格同比大幅上漲，打破了過去數年持續下行的趨勢，而中國出口產品價格的下降曾有助於抑制全球通膨。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"668\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FULnbrUmPUefAJEU4blg8g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY2OA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/c0ac36f03e81a54380f80be24dd5495b\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我在3月份能不漲價就儘量不漲，但最後還是沒辦法，」上海一家醫用導管製造商的銷售經理Pang Ling表示。「眼看著塑料成本幾乎每天都在漲，我特別著急」。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-bbfa5bdc-1b0b-35ce-8f80-e691b86dd75d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">成本壓力波及到多個行業。3月份，出口商還將泳裝、滑雪服和女褲等商品的價格上調，漲幅在1%-6%左右。這些產品高度依賴聚酯等合成纖維，而供應商該月幾乎每天都在上調纖維價格。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">其他依賴橡膠、塑料以及石油衍生化學品的產品價格也在飆升。其中，注射器是受衝擊最嚴重的產品之一，3月價格漲幅高達20%。與此同時，由於金屬和半導體成本上漲，家用電器價格受到雙重衝擊。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：一些中國出口商開始漲價 因伊朗戰爭導致成本增加</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些細分數據較早地體現出伊朗戰爭引發的能源衝擊如何波及到全球第二大經濟體，並最終影響到世界各地的零售商。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">近三年來，由於產能過剩和市場競爭激烈，中國出口價格持續下降，有助於歐美等經濟體抑制通膨。據凱投宏觀估算，近年來中國出口產品價格的下降，將發達經濟體的整體通膨率拉低約0.3至0.5個百分點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">就在今年2月，價格更低廉的中國商品還起到了緩解英國等經濟體通膨壓力的作用。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但如今，隨著中國製造商開始將更高的成本轉嫁出去，這種抑制通膨的緩衝作用開始弱化。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"632\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jgachfKS6ypX2j.Ai.4KUw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/4c30d4f44508787664681fdb36e4735e\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Inflation Looms as China’s Exporters Boost Prices on Iran Costs</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Jinshan Hong、Paul Abelsky.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
